    "headline": "T-Mobile Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend",
    "summary": "BELLEVUE, Wash., June 16, 2026--T-Mobile US, Inc. (NASDAQ: TMUS) (\"T-Mobile\" or \"the Company\") announced today that the Company’s Board of Directors has declared a cash dividend of $1.02 per share on its issued and outstanding shares of common stock. The dividend is payable on September 10, 2026 to stockholders of record as of the close of business on August 28, 2026.",
